title: Ostrich in Space - AutoRigging a Blender Model with Character Creator 4 and iClone 8
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/auto-rig.html 
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/blender.html Get ready to soar into space with the help of 3D character designer Tom Breuer! In this insightful YouTube video, Breuer shares his streamlined workflow for creating a super fly ostrich that's out of this world, using the powerful combination of Character Creator, Blender, and iClone. With the lightning-fast CC AccuRIG tool, you can turbocharge your character preparation process for animation and customize auto-rigging steps that give you complete creative control. 

Plus, you can easily add spring bones and cloth simulation to make your animated accessories even more awesome! And with AccuLips, precise lip-sync animation has never been easier. So buckle up and get ready for an epic ride as Breuer takes you on a journey through the Reallusion-Blender pipeline, proving that anything is possible when you create your own little world! https://magazine.reallusion.com/2023/04/19/ostrich-in-space-autorigging-a-blender-model-with-character-creator-4-and-iclone-8/

00:00 Opening
00:17 Character Concept
00:33 Modeling Process
01:29 Texturing in Substance Painter
01:55 Rigging with CC AccuRIG in Character Creator
03:10 Adding Custom Bones in Blender
04:00 Skin Weight Transfer
04:57 Adding More Bones in Blender & Character Creator
05:10 Making Facial Expressions
06:29 Animating Dynamic Accessories in Character Creator: Adding Spring Bones & Cloth Simulation
07:38 Animating in iClone
08:34 Create Animated Accessories: Adding Spring Bones
09:06 Animation Clips & Lip-Sync Animation with AccuLips 
09:26 Wrap-Up & Final Animation

*Tom Breuer* is a dynamic and talented freelance 3D designer with a particular flair for Blender and Unity in game-based applications and character creation. With ardent storytelling, he has created a whole world filled with fascinating 3D creatures with unique backstories that he loves to share. You can explore Breuer's stunning creatures thriving in their natural habitats by visiting his pages listed below.

▪ Sketchfab: https://sketchfab.com/TomBreuer
▪ ArtStation: https://www.artstation.com/flyingillustration
▪ Twitter: https://twitter.com/flyingillu
▪ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/flyingillustration/

Voice actor of Ostrich: *Vincent Fallow*
▪ Twitter: https://twitter.com/vincentfallow
▪ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/vincentfallow/

Character Creator 4 (CC4) connects industry leading pipelines ,such as iClone, Maya, Blender, Unreal Engine, Unity, with one system for 3D character generation, animation rig, asset management, look-dev rendering, and interactive design.

iClone is the fastest real-time 3D animation software in the industry. Integrated with groundbreaking real-time technologies, iClone simplifies the world of 3D Animation in a user-friendly production environment that blends character animation, scene design and cinematic storytelling; quickly turning imagination into a reality.

Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

title: Create Character Animation with Unity HDRP and iClone  - Jasper Hesseling @mastjappa
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/auto-setup/unity/default.html

Experienced 3D artist Jasper Hesseling shares his iClone-to-Unity workflow, using the Auto Setup plugin to seamlessly transfer his CC4-based character, Lynn, to Unity for HDRP rendering with realistic digital human shaders. By leveraging the animation previews in Unity Auto Setup and Reallusion's Parkour motion pack, he creates an impressive action sequence, complete with lifelike facial expressions.

In this video, Jasper guides viewers through each critical step and provides valuable insights into creating his “secret agent”. He showcases the versatility of the Character Creator pipeline and also incorporates other powerful 3D tools such as Marvelous Designer, Substance Painter, KitBash3D, Cascadeur, and ZBrush.

title: Outro Lite
Meet “Susan”, a Realistic Digital Human with Dynamic Wrinkles | Character Creator & iClone
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/dynamic-wrinkle.html
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/3d-content.html Toy with three hyper-realistic CC4 avatars, “Susan”, “Kevin”, and “Camila”, while wielding the power of dynamic wrinkles and extended facial profiles. Backed by more than 140 morphs, these characters are completely free to use in Character Creator 4 and iClone 8. Susan is the perfect example of Reallusion’s Mesh-to-CC technology that can accurately map original scan models from TexturingXYZ onto CC3+ character meshes. Learn to use the illustrious tools in iClone like Face Puppet, Face Key Editor, and Live Face to adjust facial expressions. Live Face, in particular, is a free facial mocap application that is robust and packed with features.

With the advanced real-time blended dynamic wrinkles and look-at constraints, Susan can seamlessly perform lip-sync animation with natural body movements and facial nuances. Users can take advantage of Character Creator 4 and iClone 8 to personalize over 300 expression morphs with modeling sliders. Plus, all styling and makeup content listed below comes included with the software. Access a wealth of options from the Reallusion asset collections, including 3D hair, skin textures, and clothes, to create unique stories for Susan.

*I.Embedded FREE dynamic wrinkles*
▪ 2 Individualized Wrinkles: Susan | Kevin 
▪ 2 Generalized Wrinkles: Neutral | Camila

*II.Embedded FREE content*
▪ Atmosphere and Lightroom: 100+ presets
▪ Lens Flare:10+preset and 30+elements
▪ Preview Animations: 40+ Preview Motions
▪ Expression Morph Sliders: 300+ expression morphs (categorized by facial feature).

▪ Hair: 10+ styles
▪ Outfit: 80+ clothes
▪ Accessory: 10+ items
▪ Skin: 90+ presets
▪ Makeup: 70+ presets

Find out more resource on our Forum post “Where to Find New Wrinkle Assets”: https://forum.reallusion.com/532894/Character-Creator-42-Arrived-Where-to-Find-New-Wrinkle-Assets-Free-Embedded-Content 

Character Creator 4 (CC4) connects industry leading pipelines ,such as iClone, Maya, Blender, Unreal Engine, Unity, with one system for 3D character generation, animation rig, asset management, look-dev rendering, and interactive design.

iClone is the fastest real-time 3D animation software in the industry. Integrated with groundbreaking real-time technologies, iClone simplifies the world of 3D Animation in a user-friendly production environment that blends character animation, scene design and cinematic storytelling; quickly turning imagination into a reality.

Le complexe résidentiel LA CITE DES ARTS, de par son emplacement, son concept original et son architecture, s’impose comme l’ultime adresse, pour tous les amateurs de confort et d’art de vivre. S’étendant sur une superficie de 6,2 Ha, le projet LA CITE DES ARTS développe des immeubles en R+5 implantés autour d’une place centrale et d’allées piétonnes.

title: VERIVERY - 'Crazy Like That' Official M/V
description:
VERIVERY – A Trendy Icon Acknowledged by All
With the release of [Liminality – EP.LOVE] last November, VERIVERY had managed to sweep multiple awards from ceremonies on top of achieving first place on music programs.

And in May 2023, VERIVERY returns with their second story through [Liminality – EP.DREAM].
 
DREAM: The Second Element of Happiness
In [Liminality – EP.LOVE], VERIVERY had expressed the emotion of ‘love’ through a number of different ways. This time, through [Liminality – EP.DREAM], VERIVERY shows off their intuitive, unique colors in the process of achieving their DREAM.

To PLAY in the Present, or PLAN for the Future
VERIVERY plans to show two different paths towards their DREAM.
With the ‘PLAY’ version emphasizing one’s happiness in the moment, and ‘PLAN’ version focusing on meticulously preparing for their future, the members will appeal to all through two contrasting sides.
The jacket expresses the journey towards a DREAM through both a ‘PLAY’-focused path, bringing energy to a chaotic yet humble space, and a ‘PLAN’-focused path, where building a blueprint for the future is portrayed in a mature, intellectual way. 
As well, the music video shows the members striving towards their DREAM in both unrestrained strides and steady, passionate steps to show the qualities unique to each of the two paths. As each of their individual spaces come together to create a common area, the members also come together in making the achievement of their DREAM a common goal.

Liminality - EP. DREAM, the Expansion of VERIVERY
Through the [Liminality - EP.DREAM] album, VERIVERY brings to light their ever-expanding musical spectrum. Through new styles of music, performance, and visuals, the group promises to show off yet another distinct, artistic side to them.
VERIVERY welcomes all into their space filled with their DREAM, so that we could all step into and explore their ‘DREAM’ home using their unique key.

모두가 인정한 트렌드 아이콘, 베리베리
지난 11월 [Liminality - EP.LOVE] 앨범을 통해 음악 방송 1위는 물론, 각종 시상식에서 상을 받으며 좋은 성과를 보여준 베리베리. 
2023년 5월, 그 두 번째 이야기 [Liminality - EP.DREAM]을 선보인다.
 
두 번째 행복의 요소, DREAM
[Liminality - EP.LOVE]를 통해 ‘사랑’이라는 감정을 표현하는 다양한 방법을 보여 주었던 베리베리. 이번 앨범 [Liminality - EP.DREAM]에서는 감각적이고 유니크한 베리베리만의 색깔로 꿈(DREAM)을 이루는 각자의 과정을 보여준다.

현재를 즐기는 PLAY, 미래를 그리는 PLAN
베리베리는 꿈(DREAM)을 향한 여정을 두 가지 방향으로 전달할 예정이다. 
현재의 행복을 중요시하는 ‘PLAY’ 버전과, 미래를 철저하게 준비하고 계획하는 ‘PLAN’ 버전으로 나누어 그들의 각기 상반된 매력을 보여주고자 한다.
자켓에서는 현재의 꿈(DREAM), ‘PLAY’에 집중한 모습을 험블하고 무질서한 공간에서 에너지 있게 보여주기도 하고, 미래의 꿈(DREAM)을 위해 ‘PLAN’하는 모습을 지적이고 섹시하게 표현한다.
뮤직비디오에서는 꿈(DREAM)을 향해 달려가는 과정을 자유분방하게 이루어 나가는 모습과, 끈기와 열정으로 이루어 나가는 모습을 동시에 보여주며 서로 다른 개성을 표현한다. 각자의 공간을 만들지만 결국 하나로 어우러지는 아지트에서, 멤버들은 꿈(DREAM)을 쫓는다는 공동의 목표를 보여줄 예정이다.

베리베리의 확장, Liminality - EP.DREAM
베리베리는 이번 앨범 [Liminality - EP.DREAM]을 통해 더욱 넓어진 그들의 음악적 스펙트럼을 보여준다. 새로운 스타일의 곡과 퍼포먼스, 비주얼을 통해 더 새롭고 아티스틱한 모습을 보여줄 예정이다.
베리베리의 소중한 꿈(DREAM)이 담긴 공간으로 모두를 초대한다. 하나뿐인 열쇠로 꿈(DREAM)의 집을 열어 베리베리의 꿈(DREAM)이 담긴 공간으로 들어가 보자.

title: Vegan TAQUITOS That Are Baked And Full Of Flavor!
description:
Crispy vegan baked taquitos which are super easy to make, gluten-free, and delicious. These meat-free flautas are filled with a hearty veggie mixture that is bursting with flavor. Enjoy this simple rolled taco recipe as a snack, dinner or side dish! 😍

Printable recipe with instructions, substitutes, nutrition facts, and lots of helpful tips:
https://elavegan.com/easy-vegan-taquitos/

📩 Want FREE RECIPES and meal plans delivered to your inbox? Sign up for my newsletter at no cost 👉 https://tinyurl.com/elavegan

🌱 100 vegan AND gluten-free recipes for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and dessert, including sides, snacks, soups, sauces, salads, and bread - all with beautiful pictures, I took myself!
🌱 Metric and imperial measurements (cups, ounces, and grams).
🌱 Refined sugar-free and allergy-friendly recipes with substitutions for any irritating ingredients.

You can order it here: https://elavegan.com/cookbooks/

INGREDIENTS:
 
2 medium-large (400 g) potatoes peeled and chopped
1/2 tbsp oil

3 garlic cloves minced

1 tsp curry powder
1 tsp onion powder
1/2 tsp ground cumin
1/4 tsp ground nutmeg
3/4-1 tsp sea salt or less/more to taste
1/4 tsp smoked paprika
Red pepper flakes to taste
Black pepper to taste
1/4 cup (60 ml) vegetable broth
5 oz (140 g) vegan cheese of choice
Taco seasoning to sprinkle on top of taquitos (optional)
8-10 small/medium tortillas

蒼穹盛開的藍色花朵，
面具底下是難以捉摸；
即便向著刺也要伸手，
只為她笑容不為什麼。

「塔莉亞」是希臘九大繆思女神之ㄧ，手握「花與面具」。將充滿詩意的象徵元素作為歌曲創作靈感，敘述男孩仰望著如女神般心儀的她，就算明知這份美麗藏著危險與刺，也心甘情願為之臣服。

新生代最強唱作團體U:NUS，於《Reborn To be Alive》巡迴Showcase第二站 ── 台北，驚喜發表首支R&B全創作單曲《塔莉亞》（Thalia），透過精心編排的舞台表演與性感舞蹈，首度嘗試成熟魅力的表演風格，引起全場粉絲的熱烈迴響、陷入瘋狂。《塔莉亞》作為U:NUS發表的第三首作品，團員透過細膩的歌詞和與過往截然不同的曲風，展現更加純熟的唱腔與聲音表情，編曲元素更加入具千禧年代感性的電吉他solo與留聲機效果，加上男孩們如在耳邊溫柔呢喃的說唱，打造如同文藝愛情電影般的浪漫氛圍歌曲。

風格多變的U:NUS，再次突破了音樂創作的界限、為音樂之路添上嶄新色彩，也讓人更加期待未來他們將帶來什麼樣的驚喜！

title: Groupe Scolaire Atlas
description:
6 raisons d'intégrer le GSA :

1- Une excellente méthodologie qui a fait ses preuves (100% de réussite au bac avec 90% de mentions Bien et T. Bien)
2. Une école centrée sur l'enfant
3- Une équipe pédagogique accomplie
4- Des moyens pédagogiques de pointe
5- Une porte ouverte aux études supérieures
6- Un réseau des anciens florissant

Bienvenue au Groupe Scolaire Atlas (GSA), un institut d’enseignement privé inauguré en 1997.

Notre mission est d'aider les enfants à devenir des penseurs confiants et indépendants qui font preuve de connaissance de soi et du monde autour d'eux, de respect et d'empathie pour les autres.

Le GSA adopte un programme académique scientifique et technologique qui développe chez l'enfant les compétences pour faire face aux défis du 21e siècle, notamment :
- la capacité de questionnement
- la réflexion
- la méthodologie de résolution de problèmes
- la communication efficace
- la créativité
- les intelligences multiples ; dont les intelligences émotionnelle, sociale et spirituelle.
